<lb n="0060a13" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0060a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060a15" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1586 [No. 1587; cf. No. 1585]</head>
<lb n="0060a16" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"/><jhead>唯識三十論<note n="0060005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">Tri&mdotabv;&sacute;ik&amacron; vij&ntilde;aptik&amacron;rik&amacron;.〔頌〕－【三】</note><note n="0060005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">Tri&mdotabv;&sacute;ik&amacron; vij&ntilde;aptik&amacron;rik&amacron;.，〔頌〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><foreign n="0060005" resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Tri&mdotabv;&sacute;ik&amacron; vij&ntilde;aptik&amacron;rik&amacron;.</foreign><app n="0060005"><lem wit="【大】">頌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0060a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060a18" ed="T"/><byline type="Author">世親菩薩造</byline>
<lb n="0060a19" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0060006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大唐〕－【宋】【元】，〔大〕－【明】</note><app n="0060006"><lem wit="【大】">大唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐</rdg></app>三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0060a20" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT31p0060a2001">護法等菩薩約此三十頌造《成唯識》，今略標
<lb n="0060a21" ed="T"/>所以。謂此三十頌中，初二十四行頌明唯識
<lb n="0060a22" ed="T"/>相；次一行頌明唯識性；後五行頌明唯識行
<lb n="0060a23" ed="T"/>位。就二十四行頌中，初一行半略辯唯識相；
<lb n="0060a24" ed="T"/>次二十二行半廣辯唯識相。謂外問言：「若唯
<lb n="0060a25" ed="T"/>有識，云何世間及諸聖教說有我法？」舉頌<note n="0060007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">詶＝以【明】</note><app n="0060007"><lem wit="【大】">詶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以</rdg></app>
<lb n="0060a26" ed="T"/>答，頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060a27" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060a2701" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><label>「１</label><l>由假說我法，</l><l>有種種相轉。</l>
<lb n="0060a28" ed="T"/><l>彼依<note n="0060008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">識所變 Vij&ntilde;&amacron;na-pari&ndotblw;&amacron;ma.</note><tt n="0060008" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">識所變</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vij&ntilde;&amacron;na-pari&ndotblw;&amacron;ma.</t></tt>，</l><l>此<note n="0060009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能變 Pari&ndotblw;&amacron;ma.</note><tt n="0060009" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">能變</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Pari&ndotblw;&amacron;ma.</t></tt>唯三：</l></lg>
<lb n="0060a29" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060a2901"><label>２</label><l>謂<note n="0060010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">異熟 Vip&amacron;ka.</note><tt n="0060010" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">異熟</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vip&amacron;ka.</t></tt>、<note n="0060011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">思量 Manana.</note><tt n="0060011" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">思量</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Manana.</t></tt>，</l><l>及<note n="0060012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了別境識 Vi&sdotblw;aya-vij&ntilde;apti.</note><tt n="0060012" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">了別境識</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vi&sdotblw;aya-vij&ntilde;apti.</t></tt>。」</l></lg>
<pb n="0060b" id="T31.1586.0060b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0060b0101"><note n="0060013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝此【三】</note><note n="0060013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次＝此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0060013"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">此</rdg></app>二十二行半廣辯唯識相者，由前頌文略
<lb n="0060b02" ed="T"/>標三能變，今廣明三變相。且初能變其相云
<lb n="0060b03" ed="T"/>何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b04" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b0401" rend="margin-left:0em"><l>「　初<note n="0060014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">阿賴耶識 &Amacron;laya-vij&ntilde;&amacron;na.</note><tt n="0060014" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">阿賴耶識</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;laya-vij&ntilde;&amacron;na.</t></tt>，</l><l>異熟<note n="0060015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一切種 Sarva-v&imacron;jaka.</note><tt n="0060015" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">一切種</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sarva-v&imacron;jaka.</t></tt>，</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b0501" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><label>３</label><l><note n="0060016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不可知 Asa&mdotabv;viditaka.</note><tt n="0060016" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">不可知</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Asa&mdotabv;viditaka.</t></tt><note n="0060017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">執受 Up&amacron;di.</note><tt n="0060017" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">執受</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Up&amacron;di.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0060018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處 Sth&amacron;na.</note><tt n="0060018" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">處</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sth&amacron;na.</t></tt><note n="0060019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了（別） Vij&ntilde;aptika.</note><note n="0060019" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>了（別） Vij&ntilde;aptika.</note>了常與<note n="0060020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觸 Spar&sacute;a.</note><tt n="0060020" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">觸</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Spar&sacute;a.</t></tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b06" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作意 Manask&amacron;ra.</note><tt n="0060021" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">作意</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Manask&amacron;ra.</t></tt>、<note n="0060022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受 Vit(vedan&amacron;).</note><note n="0060022" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>受 Vit(vedan&amacron;).</note>受、<note n="0060023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想 Sa&mdotabv;j&ntilde;&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060023" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">想</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sa&mdotabv;j&ntilde;&amacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">思 Cetan&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060024" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">思</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Cetan&amacron;.</t></tt>，</l><l>相應唯<note n="0060025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 Upek&sdotblw;&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060025" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">捨</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Upek&sdotblw;&amacron;.</t></tt>受。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b07" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b0701" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><label>４</label><l>是<note n="0060026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無覆無記 Artiv&rdotblw;ty&amacron;k&rdotblw;ta.</note><tt n="0060026" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">無覆無記</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Artiv&rdotblw;ty&amacron;k&rdotblw;ta.</t></tt>，</l><l>觸等亦如是，</l>
<lb n="0060b08" ed="T"/><l>睌鄏p<note n="0060027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瀑＝暴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0060027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瀑＝暴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0060027"><lem wit="【大】">瀑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">暴</rdg></app>流，</l><l>阿羅漢位<note n="0060028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 Vy&amacron;v&rdotblw;tti.</note><tt n="0060028" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">捨</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vy&amacron;v&rdotblw;tti.</t></tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0060b0901">已說初能變，第二能變其相<note n="0060029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＝去【明】</note><app n="0060029"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去</rdg></app>何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b1001" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><label>「５</label><l>次第二能變，</l><l>是識名<note n="0060030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末那 Manas.</note><tt n="0060030" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">末那</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Manas.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0060b11" ed="T"/><l>依彼轉緣彼，</l><l>思量為性相。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b12" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b1201" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><label>６</label><l>四煩惱常俱，</l><l>謂<note n="0060031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我癡 &Amacron;tma-moha.</note><tt n="0060031" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">我癡</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;tma-moha.</t></tt>、<note n="0060032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我見 &Amacron;tma-d&rdotblw;&sdotblw;&tdotblw;i.</note><tt n="0060032" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">我見</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;tma-d&rdotblw;&sdotblw;&tdotblw;i.</t></tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b13" ed="T"/><l>并<note n="0060033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我慢 &Amacron;tma-m&amacron;na.</note><tt n="0060033" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">我慢</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;tma-m&amacron;na.</t></tt>、<note n="0060034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我愛 &Amacron;tma-sneha.</note><tt n="0060034" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">我愛</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;tma-sneha.</t></tt>，</l><l>及餘觸等俱。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b1401" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><label>７</label><l><note n="0060035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">有覆無記 Nivrt&amacron;vy&amacron;krta.</note><tt n="0060035" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">有覆無記</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Nivrt&amacron;vy&amacron;krta.</t></tt>攝，</l><l>隨所生所繫，</l>
<lb n="0060b15" ed="T"/><l>阿羅漢<note n="0060036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅定 Nirodha-sam&amacron;patti.</note><tt n="0060036" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">滅定</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Nirodha-sam&amacron;patti.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0060037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">出世道 Lokottara-m&amacron;rga.</note><tt n="0060037" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">出世道</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Lokottara-m&amacron;rga.</t></tt>無有。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0060b1601">如是已說第二能變，第三能變其相云何？頌
<lb n="0060b17" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b1801" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><label>「８</label><l>次第三能變，</l><l>差別有六種，</l>
<lb n="0060b19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了境 Vi&sdotblw;aya-upalabdhi.</note><tt n="0060038" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">了境</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vi&sdotblw;aya-upalabdhi.</t></tt>為性相，</l><l>善不善俱非。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b20" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b2001" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><label>９</label><l>此<note n="0060039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心所 Caitasa.</note><tt n="0060039" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">心所</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Caitasa.</t></tt><note n="0060040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍行 Sarvatraga.</note><tt n="0060040" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">遍行</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sarvatraga.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">別境 Viniyata.</note><tt n="0060041" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">別境</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Viniyata.</t></tt>、<note n="0060042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善 Ku&sacute;ala.</note><tt n="0060042" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">善</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Ku&sacute;ala.</t></tt>、<note n="0060043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">煩惱 Kle&sacute;a.</note><tt n="0060043" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">煩惱</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Kle&sacute;a.</t></tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b21" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隨煩惱 Upakle&sacute;a.</note><tt n="0060044" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">隨煩惱</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Upakle&sacute;a.</t></tt>、不定，</l><l>皆三受相應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１０</label><l>初遍行觸等，</l><l>次別境謂<note n="0060045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲 Chanda.</note><tt n="0060045" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">欲</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Chanda.</t></tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勝解 Abhimok&sdotblw;a.</note><tt n="0060046" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">勝解</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Abhimok&sdotblw;a.</t></tt>、<note n="0060047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念 Sm&rdotblw;ti.</note><tt n="0060047" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">念</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sm&rdotblw;ti.</t></tt>、<note n="0060048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">定 Sam&amacron;dhi.</note><tt n="0060048" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">定</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sam&amacron;dhi.</t></tt>、<note n="0060049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慧 Dh&imacron;(praj&ntilde;&amacron;).</note><note n="0060049" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>慧 Dh&imacron;(praj&ntilde;&amacron;).</note>慧，</l><l>所緣事不同。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b24" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b2401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１１</label><l>善謂<note n="0060050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">信 &Sacute;raddh&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060050" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">信</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Sacute;raddh&amacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慚 Hr&imacron;.</note><tt n="0060051" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">慚</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Hr&imacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愧 Apatrap&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060052" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">愧</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Apatrap&amacron;.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無貪 Alobha，無瞋 Adve&sacute;a，無癡 Amoha.</note>無貪等三根，</l>
<lb n="0060b25" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勤 V&imacron;rya.</note><tt n="0060054" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">勤</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">V&imacron;rya.</t></tt>、<note n="0060055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安（輕安） Pra&sacute;rabdhi.</note><note n="0060055" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>安（輕安） Pra&sacute;rabdhi.</note>安、<note n="0060056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不放逸行 Apram&amacron;da.</note><note n="0060056" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>不放逸行 Apram&amacron;da.</note>不放逸、</l><l>行<note n="0060057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 (upek&sdotblw;&amacron;)</note><tt n="0060057" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">捨</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">(upek&sdotblw;&amacron;)</t></tt>及<note n="0060058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不害 Ahi&mdotabv;s&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060058" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">不害</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Ahi&mdotabv;s&amacron;.</t></tt>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b2601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１２</label><l>煩惱謂<note n="0060059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">貪 R&amacron;ga.</note><tt n="0060059" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">貪</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">R&amacron;ga.</t></tt>、<note n="0060060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瞋 Pratigha.</note><tt n="0060060" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">瞋</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Pratigha.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">癡 M&umacron;&ddotblw;ha.</note><tt n="0060061" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">癡</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">M&umacron;&ddotblw;ha.</t></tt>、<note n="0060062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慢 M&amacron;na.</note><tt n="0060062" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">慢</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">M&amacron;na.</t></tt>、<note n="0060063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">疑 Vicikits&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060063" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">疑</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vicikits&amacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡見 D&rdotblw;&sacute;(mithy&amacron; d&rdotblw;&sdotblw;&tdotblw;i).</note><note n="0060064" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>惡見 D&rdotblw;&sacute;(mithy&amacron; d&rdotblw;&sdotblw;&tdotblw;i).</note>惡見。</l>
<lb n="0060b27" ed="T"/><l>隨煩惱謂<note n="0060065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忿 Krodha.</note><tt n="0060065" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">忿</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Krodha.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恨 Upan&amacron;ha.</note><tt n="0060066" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">恨</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Upan&amacron;ha.</t></tt>、<note n="0060067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覆 Mrak&sdotblw;a.</note><tt n="0060067" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">覆</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Mrak&sdotblw;a.</t></tt>、<note n="0060068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惱 Prad&amacron;&sacute;a.</note><tt n="0060068" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">惱</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Prad&amacron;&sacute;a.</t></tt>、<note n="0060069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嫉 II&rdotblw;&sdotblw;y&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060069" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">嫉</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">II&rdotblw;&sdotblw;y&amacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慳 M&amacron;tsarya.</note><tt n="0060070" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">慳</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">M&amacron;tsarya.</t></tt>、</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b28" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060b2801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１３</label><l><note n="0060071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誑 &Sacute;&amacron;&tdotblw;hya.</note><tt n="0060071" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">誑</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Sacute;&amacron;&tdotblw;hya.</t></tt><note n="0060072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諂 (m&amacron;y&amacron;).</note>、<tt n="0060072" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">諂</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">(m&amacron;y&amacron;).</t></tt>與<note n="0060073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">害 Vihi&mdotabv;s&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060073" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">害</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vihi&mdotabv;s&amacron;.</t></tt>、<note n="0060074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">憍 Mada.</note><tt n="0060074" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">憍</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Mada.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060075" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無慚 &Amacron;hr&imacron;(&amacron;hr&imacron;kya).</note><note n="0060075" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>無慚 &Amacron;hr&imacron;(&amacron;hr&imacron;kya).</note>無慚及<note n="0060076" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無愧 Atrap&amacron;(anapatrap&amacron;ya).</note><note n="0060076" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>無愧 Atrap&amacron;(anapatrap&amacron;ya).</note>無愧、</l>
<lb n="0060b29" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060077" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掉舉 Auddhatya.</note><tt n="0060077" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">掉舉</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Auddhatya.</t></tt>與<note n="0060078" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惛＝昏【三】【宮】，惛沈 Sty&amacron;na.</note><note n="0060078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惛沈 Sty&amacron;na.，惛＝昏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><tt n="0060078" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi"><app n="0060078"><lem wit="【大】">惛沈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">昏沈</rdg></app></t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sty&amacron;na.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060079" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不信 &Amacron;&sacute;raddhya.</note><tt n="0060079" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">不信</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;&sacute;raddhya.</t></tt>并<note n="0060080" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懈怠 Kau&sacute;&imacron;dya.</note><tt n="0060080" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">懈怠</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Kau&sacute;&imacron;dya.</t></tt>、</l></lg>
<pb n="0060c" id="T31.1586.0060c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060c01" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060c0101" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１４</label><l><note n="0060081" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">放逸 Pram&amacron;da.</note><tt n="0060081" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">放逸</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Pram&amacron;da.</t></tt>及<note n="0060082" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">失念 Mu&sdotblw;&tdotblw;a-sm&rdotblw;&tdotblw;ati.</note><tt n="0060082" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">失念</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Mu&sdotblw;&tdotblw;a-sm&rdotblw;&tdotblw;ati.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0060083" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散亂 Vik&sdotblw;epa.</note><tt n="0060083" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">散亂</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vik&sdotblw;epa.</t></tt>、<note n="0060084" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不正知 Asamprajanya.</note><tt n="0060084" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">不正知</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Asamprajanya.</t></tt>。</l>
<lb n="0060c02" ed="T"/><l>不定謂<note n="0060085" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悔（惡作） Kauk&rdotblw;tya.</note><note n="0060085" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>悔（惡作） Kauk&rdotblw;tya.</note>悔、<note n="0060086" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眠 Middha.</note><tt n="0060086" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">眠</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Middha.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0060087" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尋 Vitarka.</note><tt n="0060087" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">尋</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vitarka.</t></tt>、<note n="0060088" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">伺 Vic&amacron;ra.</note><tt n="0060088" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">伺</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vic&amacron;ra.</t></tt>二各二。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0060c0301">已說六識心所相應，云何應知現起分位？頌
<lb n="0060c04" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0060c05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060c0501" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「１５</label><l>依止<note n="0060089" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">根本識 M&umacron;la-vij&ntilde;&amacron;na</note><tt n="0060089" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">根本識</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">M&umacron;la-vij&ntilde;&amacron;na</t></tt>，</l><l>五識隨緣現，</l>
<lb n="0060c06" ed="T"/><l>或俱或不俱，</l><l>如濤波依水。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c07" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0060c0701" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>１６</label><l><note n="0060090" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意識 Manas.</note><tt n="0060090" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">意識</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Manas.</t></tt>常現起，</l><l>除生<note n="0060091" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無想天 &Amacron;sa&mdotabv;j&ntilde;ika.</note><tt n="0060091" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">無想天</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">&Amacron;sa&mdotabv;j&ntilde;ika.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0060c08" ed="T"/><l>及<note n="0060092" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無心二定（無想定） Asa&mdotabv;j&ntilde;i-sam&amacron;patti.（滅盡定） nirodha-sam&amacron;patti.</note>無心二定，</l><l><note n="0060093" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">睡眠 (acittaka).</note><tt n="0060093" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">睡眠</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">(acittaka).</t></tt>與<note n="0060094" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悶絕 M&umacron;rcch&amacron;.</note><tt n="0060094" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">悶絕</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">M&umacron;rcch&amacron;.</t></tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0060c0901">已廣分別三能變相為自所變二分所依，云
<lb n="0060c10" ed="T"/>何應知依識所變假說我、法非別實有，<note n="0060095" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">由＝猶【三】</note><note n="0060095" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＝猶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0060095"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>斯
<pb n="0061a" id="T31.1586.0061a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0061a01" ed="T"/>一切唯有識耶？頌<note n="0061001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0061001"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0061a02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a0201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「１７</label><l>是諸識轉變，</l><l><note n="0061002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分別 Vikalpa.</note><tt n="0061002" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">分別</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vikalpa.</t></tt>、所分別，</l>
<lb n="0061a03" ed="T"/><l>由此彼皆無，</l><l>故一切<note n="0061003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯識 Vij&ntilde;apti-m&amacron;traka.</note><tt n="0061003" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">唯識</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vij&ntilde;apti-m&amacron;traka.</t></tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061a0401">若唯有識，都無外緣，由何而生種種分別？頌
<lb n="0061a05" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a0601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「１８</label><l>由一切種識，</l><l>如是如是變，</l>
<lb n="0061a07" ed="T"/><l>以<note n="0061004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">展轉力 Anyo'nyava&sacute;a.</note><tt n="0061004" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">展轉力</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Anyo'nyava&sacute;a.</t></tt>故，</l><l>彼彼分別生。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061a0801">雖有內識而無外緣，由何有情生死相續？頌
<lb n="0061a09" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a1001" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「１９</label><l>由諸<note n="0061005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">業習氣 Karma-v&amacron;&sacute;an&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061005" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">業習氣</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Karma-v&amacron;&sacute;an&amacron;.</t></tt>、</l><l><note n="0061006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二取 Gr&amacron;hadvaya（我執習氣 gr&amacron;hya-gr&amacron;ha，名言習氣 gr&amacron;haka-gr&amacron;ha）.</note>二取習氣俱，</l>
<lb n="0061a11" ed="T"/><l>前異熟既盡，</l><l>復生餘異熟。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061a1201">若唯有識，何故世尊處處經中說有三性？應
<lb n="0061a13" ed="T"/>知三性亦不離識，所以者何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a1401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２０</label><l>由彼彼遍計，</l><l>遍計種種物，</l>
<lb n="0061a15" ed="T"/><l>此<note n="0061007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍計所執 Parikalpita.</note><tt n="0061007" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">遍計所執</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Parikalpita.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0061008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自性 Svabh&amacron;va.</note><tt n="0061008" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">自性</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Svabh&amacron;va.</t></tt>無所有。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a16" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a1601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>２１</label><l><note n="0061009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依他起自性 Paratantra-svabh&amacron;va.</note><tt n="0061009" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">依他起自性</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Paratantra-svabh&amacron;va.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0061010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分別緣所生 Vikalpa&hdotblw; pratyayodbhava&hdotblw;.</note><tt n="0061010" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">分別緣所生</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Vikalpa&hdotblw; pratyayodbhava&hdotblw;.</t></tt>。</l>
<lb n="0061a17" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">圓成實性 Ni&sdotblw;panna(parini&sdotblw;panna).</note><note n="0061011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="u"/>圓成實性 Ni&sdotblw;panna(parini&sdotblw;panna).</note>圓成實於彼，</l><l>常遠離前性。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a1801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>２２</label><l>故此與依他，</l><l>非異非不異，</l>
<lb n="0061a19" ed="T"/><l>如無常等性，</l><l><note n="0061012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">非不見此彼 （&M062419;&M062476;&M062482;&M062463;&M062426;&M062423;&M062438;&M062411;&M062476;&M062433;&M062463;&M062475;&M062466;&M062446;&M062443;&M062402;&M062473;&M062426;）N&amacron;d&rdotblw;&sdotblw;&tdotblw;e asmin(parini&sdotblw;panne)sa (paratantra-svabh&amacron;vo)d&rdotblw;&sacute;yate.</note>非不見此彼。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061a2001">若有三性，如何世尊說一切法皆無自性？頌
<lb n="0061a21" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２３</label><l>即依此三性，</l><l>立彼<note n="0061013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三無性 Trividh&amacron; ni&hdotblw;svabh&amacron;vat&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061013" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">三無性</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Trividh&amacron; ni&hdotblw;svabh&amacron;vat&amacron;.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a23" ed="T"/><l>故佛密意說，</l><l><note n="0061014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一切法無性 Sarva-dharm&amacron;n&amacron;&mdotabv; ni&hdotblw;svabh&amacron;vat&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061014" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">一切法無性</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sarva-dharm&amacron;n&amacron;&mdotabv; ni&hdotblw;svabh&amacron;vat&amacron;.</t></tt>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a24" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a2401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>２４</label><l>初即<note n="0061015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相 Lak&sdotblw;a&ndotblw;a.</note><tt n="0061015" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">相</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Lak&sdotblw;a&ndotblw;a.</t></tt>無性，</l><l>次無<note n="0061016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自然性 Svaya&mdotabv;bh&amacron;va.</note><tt n="0061016" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">自然性</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Svaya&mdotabv;bh&amacron;va.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a25" ed="T"/><l>後由遠離前，</l><l>所執我、法性。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061a2601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><label>２５</label><l>此<note n="0061017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諸法勝義 Dharm&amacron;n&amacron;m param&amacron;rtha.</note><tt n="0061017" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">諸法勝義</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Dharm&amacron;n&amacron;m param&amacron;rtha.</t></tt>，</l><l>亦即是<note n="0061018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">真如 Tathat&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061018" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">真如</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Tathat&amacron;.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a27" ed="T"/><note n="0061019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當如其性故即唯識實性 Sarvak&amacron;'a&mdotabv; tath&amacron;bh&amacron;v&amacron;t saiva vij&ntilde;aptim&amacron;trat&amacron;.</note><note n="0061019" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.say">常</lem><rdg wit="【大】">當</rdg></app>如其性故即唯識實性 Sarvak&amacron;'a&mdotabv; tath&amacron;bh&amacron;v&amacron;t saiva vij&ntilde;aptim&amacron;trat&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061019" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi"><l>常如其性故，</l><l>即唯識實性。」</l></t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sarvak&amacron;'a&mdotabv; tath&amacron;bh&amacron;v&amacron;t saiva vij&ntilde;aptim&amacron;trat&amacron;.</t></tt></lg>
<lb n="0061a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061a2801">後<note n="0061020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝三【元】【明】</note><app n="0061020"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>行頌明唯識行位者，論曰：「如是所成唯
<lb n="0061a29" ed="T"/>識性、相，誰依幾位？如何悟入？」謂具大乘二種
<pb n="0061b" id="T31.1586.0061b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0061b01" ed="T"/>種性：一、本性種性，謂無始來依附本識，法爾
<lb n="0061b02" ed="T"/>所得無漏法因；二、謂習所成種性，謂聞法界
<lb n="0061b03" ed="T"/>等流法已，聞所成<note n="0061021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔等薰習所成〕－【三】</note><note n="0061021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔等<app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">熏</lem><rdg wit="【大】">薰</rdg></app>習所成〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061021"><lem wit="【大】">等熏習所成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。具此二性
<lb n="0061b04" ed="T"/>方能悟入。何謂五位？一、資糧位，謂修大乘順
<lb n="0061b05" ed="T"/>解脫分，依識性、相能深信解。其相云何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0061b06" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061b0601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２６</label><l>乃至未起識，</l><l>求住唯識性，</l>
<lb n="0061b07" ed="T"/><l>於二取隨眠，</l><l><note n="0061022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">Y&amacron;vad vij&ntilde;apti-m&amacron;tratve vij&ntilde;&amacron;na&mdotabv; n&amacron;vati&sdotblw;&tdotblw;hati | gr&amacron;hadvayasy&amacron;nu&sacute;ayas t&amacron;van vini vartate ||</note><foreign n="0061022" resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Y&amacron;vad vij&ntilde;apti-m&amacron;tratve vij&ntilde;&amacron;na&mdotabv; n&amacron;vati&sdotblw;&tdotblw;hati | gr&amacron;hadvayasy&amacron;nu&sacute;ayas t&amacron;van vini vartate ||</foreign>猶未能伏滅。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061b0801">二、加行位，謂修大乘順決擇分，在加行<note n="0061023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">位＝謂【三】</note><note n="0061023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">位＝謂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061023"><lem wit="【大】">位</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">謂</rdg></app>能
<lb n="0061b09" ed="T"/>漸伏除所取、能取。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061b1001" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２７</label><l>現前立少物，</l><l>謂是唯識性，</l>
<lb n="0061b11" ed="T"/><l>以有所得故，</l><l>非實住唯識。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061b1201">三、通達位，謂諸菩薩所<note n="0061024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝位【三】</note><note n="0061024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝位【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061024"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">位</rdg></app>見道，在通達位如
<lb n="0061b13" ed="T"/>實通達。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b14" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061b1401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２８</label><note n="0061025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若時於所緣智都無所得 Yad&amacron; tv &amacron;lambana&mdotabv; vij&ntilde;&amacron;na&mdotabv; naivopalabhate tad&amacron;.</note><tt n="0061025" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi"><l rend="margin-left:0em">若時於所緣，</l><l>智都無所得，</l></t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Yad&amacron; tv &amacron;lambana&mdotabv; vij&ntilde;&amacron;na&mdotabv; naivopalabhate tad&amacron;.</t></tt>
<lb n="0061b15" ed="T"/><l>爾時住唯識，</l><l>離二取相故。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061b1601">四、修習位，謂諸菩薩所住修道，修習位中如
<lb n="0061b17" ed="T"/>實見理，數數修習。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061b1801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「２９</label><note n="0061026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無得不思議 Acintyo'nupalambha&hdotblw;</note><l><tt n="0061026" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">無得不思議</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Acintyo'nupalambha&hdotblw;</t></tt>，</l><l>是<note n="0061027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">出世間智 Lakottara-j&ntilde;&amacron;na.</note><tt n="0061027" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">出世間智</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Lakottara-j&ntilde;&amacron;na.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061b19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨&CB00308;重 Dau&sdotblw;&tdotblw;hulyah&amacron;ni.</note>捨二&CB00308;重故，</l><l>便證得<note n="0061029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉依 &Amacron;&sacute;rayasya par&amacron;v&rdotblw;tti&hdotblw; （變住 mvp. 131）</note>轉依。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT31p0061b2001">五、究竟位，謂住無上正等菩提，出障圓明，能
<lb n="0061b21" ed="T"/>盡未來化有情類。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b22" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT31p0061b2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><label>「３０</label><l>此即<note n="0061030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無漏界 An&amacron;&sacute;rav&imacron; dh&amacron;tu&hdotblw;.</note><tt n="0061030" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">無漏界</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">An&amacron;&sacute;rav&imacron; dh&amacron;tu&hdotblw;.</t></tt>，</l><l>不思議<note n="0061031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善 Ku&sacute;ala.</note><tt n="0061031" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">善</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Ku&sacute;ala.</t></tt><note n="0061032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常 Dhruva.</note><tt n="0061032" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">常</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Dhruva.</t></tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061b23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安樂解脫身 Sukh&imacron;vimukti-k&amacron;ya&hdotblw;.</note><tt n="0061033" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">安樂解脫身</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Sukh&imacron;vimukti-k&amacron;ya&hdotblw;.</t></tt>，</l><l><note n="0061034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大牟尼名法 Dharm&amacron;khyo 'yam mah&amacron;mune&hdotblw;.</note><tt n="0061034" type="app"><t resp="Taisho" lang="chi">大牟尼名法</t><t resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">Dharm&amacron;khyo 'yam mah&amacron;mune&hdotblw;.</t></tt>。」</l></lg></div1>
